@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam sequence {
  ArrowColor Black
  LifeLineBorderColor Black
  LifeLineBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantBorderColor Black
  ParticipantBackgroundColor White
  ActorBorderColor Black
  ActorBackgroundColor White
  ParticipantFontColor Black
  ActorFontColor Black
}

actor "User" as User
participant "Frontend" as UI
participant "Backend API\nPOST /api/wallets/register" as API
participant "Database\nTable: Wallet" as DB
User->UI: Request wallet creation
UI->API: Submit wallet creation request
API->DB: Create wallet record
DB-->API: Wallet created successfully
API-->UI: Return wallet data
UI-->User: Display wallet creation result

@enduml
